data.description: This house is a hidden gem! And fresh paint make even more adorable.  A quiet street near all those amenities is quite a find. The layout is pretty neat too—two living areas and a fireplace, that's always a plus. House has three bedrooms and two bathrooms, a fireplace and a two car garage along with a fenced backyard.  Oh, it really does sound like a gem! The two-car garage and a fenced back yard is a sweet bonus.  Imagine sitting on the couch with your honey, in front of a roaring fire during the cold winter months.
